  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): split from \"Latent Space Tools\". IMPORTANT: this is Ian Johnson's\n     (@enjalot) project — clarify your actual contribution before publishing so\n     it's not miscredited. Screenshots below are from the project docs. Draft. -->\n<p class=\"\">A scientific instrument for investigating latent spaces — ingest a dataset, embed it, project with UMAP, cluster, and explore, all in one tool.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"latent-scope UMAP projection\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1780065007/projects/latent-scope/umap.png\" alt=\"latent-scope UMAP projection\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1780065007/projects/latent-scope/umap.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1780065007/projects/latent-scope/umap.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1780065007/projects/latent-scope/umap.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1780065007/projects/latent-scope/umap.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"latent-scope UMAP projection\" width=\"3130\" height=\"3414\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.1deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3130×3414\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-square w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">latent-scope UMAP projection</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"latent-scope cluster view\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1780065008/projects/latent-scope/cluster.png\" alt=\"latent-scope cluster view\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1780065008/projects/latent-scope/cluster.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1780065008/projects/latent-scope/cluster.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1780065008/projects/latent-scope/cluster.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1780065008/projects/latent-scope/cluster.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"latent-scope cluster view\" width=\"3130\" height=\"3414\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.51deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3130×3414\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-square w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">latent-scope cluster view</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"latent-scope explore view\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1780065006/projects/latent-scope/explore.png\" alt=\"latent-scope explore view\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1780065006/projects/latent-scope/explore.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1780065006/projects/latent-scope/explore.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1780065006/projects/latent-scope/explore.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1780065006/projects/latent-scope/explore.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"latent-scope explore view\" width=\"3130\" height=\"3414\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.54deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3130×3414\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-square w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">latent-scope explore view</figcaption>\n</figure>",
